              <p></p>
              <p>We try to respond to all requests within 1 (one) month. Occasionally, it may take us longer than 1 (one) month if your request is particularly complex or you have made a number of requests. In this case, we will notify you within 1 (one) month of the receipt of your request and keep you updated.          </p>
              <p>If you are not satisfied with our response to your complaint, you have the right to lodge a complaint with the Commissioner for Personal Data (CPD), the Cypriot supervisory authority for data protection issues. Alternatively, you also have the right to lodge a complaint with the data protection authority of your country of residence.            </p>
